Name: Masterchef Chinese Food Edition
About the game: Masterchef Chinese Food Edition is an exciting fast food simulation game. You just opened a chinese restaurant, let's see how fast you can satisfy your customers Even if you're not a chef, with this game you will learn step by step very fast how to do your favorite chinese food like noodles, dumplings and more. Game Features: - More than 100 combinations to prepare the dishes - 5 types of chinese food to choose to prepare: noodles, dim sum, dumplings, spring rolls and fortune cookies - Strive to make good food every time so that you can consume it in the end
